     Author: Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)
     Contributors: Claude (Anthropic)
     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Dark Glassmorphism theme. Cyan (#00BCD4)
         and teal (#009688) accents with semi-transparent surface brushes on a
         deep dark (#121212) background to simulate a glass-like frosted effect.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in DarkGlassTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

